tiers.ability_description: Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.

Whenever K-2SO attacks out of turn, K-2SO deals 150% bonus damage, inflicts Offense Down and Healing Immunity for 1 turn on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever K-2SO loses Taunt, he removes 50% Turn Meter from all enemies and inflicts Blind on them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

At the start of encounter, if Admiral Raddus is the ally in the Leader slot and all other allies are Rogue One, inflict Defense Down and Expose for 2 turns on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever Admiral Raddus uses his Basic ability, he calls another random Rogue One ally to assist. Admiral Raddus can't be defeated while K-2SO is active.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.
The first time each Unaligned Force User ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Ahsoka Tano (Fulcrum) gains Retribution, they also gain 10% Defense and 10% Health Steal (stacking, max 200%), and 10 Speed (stacking, max 200) until the end of encounter.
Whenever Dark Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are Pirates at the start of encounter, Pirate allies gain 3 stacks of Profit. Whenever Pirate allies have 15 or more combined stacks of Profit:

- Pirate Attacker allies gain Stealth for 1 turn whenever they are critically hit.
- Whenever a Pirate Tank ally uses an ability, all other Pirate allies are called to assist.
- Whenever a Pirate Support or Healer ally is inflicted with a debuff, all Pirate allies recover 5% Health and 5% Protection.

Whenever a Pirate ally consumes a stack of Profit, all Pirate allies gain 5% Defense, Max Health, Max Protection, and Offense (stacking, max 150%) for the rest of the encounter.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.

Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User critically hits an enemy, dispel all debuffs on themself and gain 5% Turn Meter. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability against an enemy with at least 3 debuffs, reduce that enemy's Max Health by 5%. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability when they have at least 3 buffs that can be dispelled, gain 5% Max Health.

Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Commander Luke Skywalker gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
Whenever enemies are damaged at the start of their turn, Unaligned Force User allies gain 2% Turn Meter.
Whenever Ben Solo deals damage to an enemy, remove 25% Turn Meter from that enemy.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain Tenacity Up, they gain Protection Up (10%, stacking) for 2 turns.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.

At the start of their turn, Healer allies inflict Healing Immunity on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or resisted. Whenever a non-Healer character is healed by an allied Healer, they reduce their cooldowns by 1.

Whenever an ally falls below 25% Health for the first time, all allies recover 50% Health and 100% Protection. The first time an ally is defeated, revive them with 50% Health and 2 stacks of Heal Over Time for 2 turns. Whenever Healer is critically hit, recover 15% Health and Protection and grant a stack of Heal Over Time to the weakest ally for 2 turns.

The first time Barriss Offee is defeated, if there is at least one other active ally, revive all other defeated allies and other allies recover +100% Health and Protection, gain 100% Turn Meter and 100% Offense until the end of battle.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Dark Side allies start the battle with Protection Up (20%) for 2 turns.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.

Count Dooku has +200% Critical Chance and Critical Damage while he is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever a Separatist ally uses a Special ability on their turn, Count Dooku assists and dispels all buffs on the target enemy.

At the end of his turn, Count Dooku is inflicted with Disarm until the start of his next turn. Whenever Count Dooku takes damage during his turn, the weakest enemy is dealt 200% of that damage, which can't defeat them.
Whenever Dark Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Whenever a debuff on an enemy expires, Attacker allies gain 2% Offense, doubled if that debuff was dispelled, until the end of battle.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
Whenever Clone Wars Chewbacca uses a Basic ability on their turn, other allies gain +25% Turn Meter.

Whenever Thrawn resists a debuff, all allies recover 10% Health and Protection, and gain 20% Health Steal (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever Thrawn attacks out of turn, he ignores Protection, and if the enemy is inflicted with Burning, Thrawn deals 100% bonus damage and removes 100% Turn Meter, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever R2-D2 uses a Basic ability, R2-D2 gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns and 50% Turn Meter. Whenever R2-D2 damages an enemy using a Special ability, inflict Fear for 1 turn on that enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.

At the start of each encounter, if there is another Support ally, Darth Nihilus gains 100% Max Health and Max Protection for the rest of the encounter.

Whenever Darth Nihilus reduces his cooldowns, for each cooldown reduced, he gains 25% Turn Meter and 50% Offense (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.

Whenever Darth Nihilus defeats an enemy, Expose all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever Darth Nihilus inflicts Damage Over Time on an enemy, all allies gain 3 stacks of Heal Over Time for 2 turns.

Whenever Darth Nihilus attacks out of turn, his cooldown for Annihilate reduces by 1.

At the start of battle, if there are no Galactic Legend allies, whenever General Kenobi Taunts, all allies gain Protection Over Time (75%) for 2 turns, and whenever he loses Taunt, all allies recover 15% Health and Protection, and gain Defense Up for 1 turn.

Whenever General Kenobi attacks during his turn, if he has Foresight, call all other allies to assist, dealing 50% more damage to the target enemy.

The first time another ally falls below 50% Health for the first time, General Kenobi Taunts for 2 turns. If he was already taunting, he gains Damage Immunity for 1 turn.

At the start of the battle, if CT-7567 "Rex" is in the Leader slot, all allies gain 200% Defense for the rest of the battle. Whenever any other ally uses a Special Ability, CT-7567 "Rex" assists.

During CT-7567 "Rex" turn, if an ally is inflicted with Daze, Stun, or Ability Block, dispel it, and inflict Protection Disruption for 2 turns on all enemies, which can't be evaded, dispelled, or resisted.

Whenever an ally is inflicted with a debuff, all allies gain 10% Turn Meter.

Whenever an ally loses a stack of Protection Over Time, they gain Foresight for 1 turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.
Whenever a Support ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the target enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Light Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.
Whenever a debuff on an enemy expires, Attacker allies gain 2% Offense, doubled if that debuff was dispelled, until the end of battle.

Whenever Resistance Trooper uses his Basic ability on his turn, he Exposes the target enemy for 2 turns. Whenever Resistance Trooper attacks an Exposed enemy, all other allies gain 20% Turn Meter, Resistance Trooper has a 50% chance to attack again and Expose a random enemy for 1 turn.

Whenever Resistance Trooper falls below 50% for the first time, he gains Damage Immunity and Health Steal Up for 2 turns and all other allies gain Evasion Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
